🖼️ AI图片生成 官方 必装 概述 Nano Banana Pro (Gemini 3 Pro Image) 文生图，2K高清配图生成，支持多种风格。专为博客文章、公众号、社交媒体配图设计。
🤖 支持模型 gemini-2.5-flash-image 快速生成，适合草稿和迭代
gemini-3-flash-preview 平衡速度和质量
gemini-3-pro-image-preview 默认模型，最佳质量
veo-3.1-fast-generate-preview 视频生成（实验性）
💻 使用方法 方式1：命令行脚本（推荐） # 进入技能目录 cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/nano-banana-pro 生成图片 uv run scripts/generate_image.py &ndash;prompt &ldquo;一只戴墨镜的可爱猫咪，赛博朋克风格，霓虹灯光&rdquo; &ndash;filename &ldquo;cyber-cat.png&rdquo; &ndash;resolution 2K
输出 图片保存到当前目录 分辨率: 2816 x 1536 (2K) 方式2：API直接调用 curl "http://zx2.52youxi.cc:3000/v1/images/generations" \ -H "Content-Type: application/json" \ -H "Authorization: Bearer sk-GseFWg0amtOfp6MdkHK7bk1nvLHb5FC5dYtFH1g7Kc2YaYVx" \ -d '{ "model": "gemini-3-pro-image-preview", "prompt": "A professional workspace with laptop and coffee, minimalist style, soft lighting", "n": 1, "size": "1024x1024" }' 响应 { &ldquo;data&rdquo;: [ { &ldquo;url&rdquo;: &ldquo;https://&hellip;/image.png&rdquo;, &ldquo;revised_prompt&rdquo;: &ldquo;优化后的提示词&rdquo; } ] }
方式3：OpenAI兼容格式 import requests response = requests.post( &ldquo;http://zx2.52youxi.cc:3000/v1/chat/completions&quot;, headers={ &ldquo;Authorization&rdquo;: &ldquo;Bearer sk-xxx&rdquo;, &ldquo;Content-Type&rdquo;: &ldquo;application/json&rdquo; }, json={ &ldquo;model&rdquo;: &ldquo;gemini-3-pro-image-preview&rdquo;, &ldquo;messages&rdquo;: [ {&ldquo;role&rdquo;: &ldquo;user&rdquo;, &ldquo;content&rdquo;: &ldquo;生成一张科技风格的博客封面图&rdquo;} ] } )
返回图片URL ⚙️ 配置 OpenClaw技能配置 # ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json { &ldquo;skills&rdquo;: { &ldquo;entries&rdquo;: { &ldquo;nano-banana-pro&rdquo;: { &ldquo;env&rdquo;: { &ldquo;GEMINI_API_KEY&rdquo;: &ldquo;sk-GseFWg0amtOfp6MdkHK7bk1nvLHb5FC5dYtFH1g7Kc2YaYVx&rdquo;, &ldquo;GEMINI_BASE_URL&rdquo;: &ldquo;http://zx2.52youxi.cc:3000&rdquo; } } } } }
环境变量方式 # ~/.zshrc 或 ~/.bashrc export GEMINI_API_KEY=&ldquo;sk-xxx&rdquo; export GEMINI_BASE_URL=&ldquo;http://zx2.52youxi.cc:3000&rdquo;
🎨 提示词技巧 博客封面图 # 技术类文章 "A futuristic data center with glowing servers, blue and purple gradient, cinematic lighting, wide angle, professional tech blog cover style" 商业分析 &ldquo;Modern office workspace with holographic charts and graphs, clean minimalist style, professional lighting, business blog cover&rdquo;
教程类 &ldquo;Step-by-step learning concept, abstract visualization of knowledge transfer, bright and inviting colors, educational blog style&rdquo;
公众号配图 # 情感类文章 "Warm sunset scene with silhouette of person thinking, soft golden hour lighting, contemplative mood, WeChat article style" 科技资讯 &ldquo;Abstract representation of AI and human collaboration, neon accents on dark background, futuristic tech news style&rdquo;
💡 提示：在提示词中包含风格描述（如"minimalist style"、"cinematic lighting"）和质量描述（如"highly detailed"、"professional"）可以获得更好的效果。 📐 分辨率选项 选项 分辨率 适用场景 1K 1408 x 768 社交媒体头像、小图 2K 2816 x 1536 博客封面、公众号配图（推荐） 4K 5632 x 3072 海报、印刷物料 🚀 批量生成 #!/bin/bash 批量生成配图 prompts=( &ldquo;科技风格封面图&rdquo; &ldquo;商务会议场景&rdquo; &ldquo;数据可视化&rdquo; &ldquo;团队协作&rdquo; )
for i in &ldquo;${!prompts[@]}&rdquo;; do uv run scripts/generate_image.py &ndash;prompt &ldquo;${prompts[$i]}, professional blog style, 2K&rdquo; &ndash;filename &ldquo;cover-$(($i+1)).png&rdquo; &ndash;resolution 2K done
